<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="slim-down">slim down</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>变苗条；(使) 减少；(使) 缩小：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>slimmed down to</strong> 60 kilos before her wedding.
婚礼前她把体重减到了60公斤。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The company is going to slim down its workforce.
这家公司要裁员。</p></div></div>